focusArea.name: AI Ethics
focusArea.description: Given your interest in AI ethics, combined with your role as a Product Manager, focusing on AI Ethics will empower you to lead ethically sound AI product development. With your background in project management and team leadership, you can influence the integration of ethical guidelines throughout the product lifecycle, ensuring responsible AI deployment. Your interest in user experience aligns with the ethical commitment to creating AI systems that respect user rights and promote fairness.
